text: "Polaroid" is a 2020 song by country singer Keith Urban and is the third single released in Australia from his 11th studio album The Speed of Now Part 1. It was released during the COVID-19 lockdown and went to number 33 on the Canadian Billboard Digital Songs chart. ==Track listings== Digital download – single # "Polaroid" – 2:30 # "God Whispered Your Name" – 3:52 ==References== Category:2020 songs Category:Country pop songs Category:Keith Urban songs
